      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>baharat </strong>to a plate with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced halloumi </strong>to the spices and turn them several times until they're fully coated</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
