      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> drained potatoes</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>coriander seeds</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to crisp</p>",
