      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> green beans</strong> to the reserved pot and cover with<strong> boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot</p>",
